{
  "video_id": "lJGtXuCmZBM",
  "title": "Shilo Shiv Suleman: Using tech to enable dreaming",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 18259.0,
      "text": "My story begins right here actually in Rajasthan"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "about two years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "I was in the desert, under the starry skies"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "with the Sufi singer Mukhtiar Ali."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 27260.0,
      "text": "And we were in conversation"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 29260.0,
      "text": "about how nothing had changed"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "since the time of the ancient Indian epic \"The Mahabharata.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 35260.0,
      "text": "So back in the day, when us Indians wanted to travel"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35260.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d jump into a chariot and we&#39;d zoom across the sky."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38260.0,
      "end_time": 41260.0,
      "text": "Now we do the same with airplanes."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41260.0,
      "end_time": 43260.0,
      "text": "Back then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43260.0,
      "end_time": 45260.0,
      "text": "when Arjuna, the great Indian warrior prince,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 47260.0,
      "text": "when he was thirsty, he&#39;d take out a bow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "he&#39;d shoot it into the ground and water would come out."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 52260.0,
      "text": "Now we do the same"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52260.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "with drills and machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54260.0,
      "end_time": 56260.0,
      "text": "The conclusion that we came to"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56260.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "was that magic had been replaced"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 60260.0,
      "text": "by machinery."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "And this made me really sad."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 66259.0,
      "text": "I found myself becoming a little bit of a technophobe."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "I was terrified by this idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 70260.0,
      "text": "that I would lose the ability"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "to enjoy and appreciate the sunset"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "without having my camera on me, without tweeting it to my friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 77260.0,
      "text": "And it felt like technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 77260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "should enable magic, not kill it."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "When I was a little girl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "my grandfather gave me his little silver pocket watch."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "And this piece of 50-year-old technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 89260.0,
      "text": "became the most magical thing to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 89260.0,
      "end_time": 91260.0,
      "text": "It became a gilded gateway"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 91260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "into a world full of pirates and shipwrecks"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "and images in my imagination."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 99260.0,
      "text": "So I felt like our cellphones"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 99260.0,
      "end_time": 101260.0,
      "text": "and our fancy watches and our cameras"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 101260.0,
      "end_time": 103260.0,
      "text": "had stopped us from dreaming."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 103260.0,
      "end_time": 105260.0,
      "text": "They stopped us from being inspired."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 105260.0,
      "end_time": 108260.0,
      "text": "And so I jumped in, I jumped into this world of technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 108260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "to see how I could use it to enable magic"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 112260.0,
      "text": "as opposed to kill it."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 114260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been illustrating books since I was 16."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 114260.0,
      "end_time": 116260.0,
      "text": "And so when I saw the iPad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 116260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "I saw it as a storytelling device"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 121260.0,
      "text": "that could connect readers all over the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 121260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "It can know how we&#39;re holding it."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "It can know where we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 128259.0,
      "text": "It brings together image and text"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 128258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "and animation and sound and touch."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 131260.0,
      "end_time": 133260.0,
      "text": "Storytelling is becoming"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 135260.0,
      "text": "more and more multi-sensorial."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 137260.0,
      "text": "But what are we doing with it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 137260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m actually just going to go in and launch Khoya,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 143260.0,
      "text": "an interactive app for the iPad."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 146260.0,
      "text": "So it says, \"Place your fingers"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 146260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "upon each light.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "And so --"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 175260.0,
      "end_time": 179260.0,
      "text": "It says, \"This box belongs to ... \""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 179260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "And so I type in my name."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "And actually I become a character in the book."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 186260.0,
      "text": "At various points, a little letter drops down to me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 186260.0,
      "end_time": 189260.0,
      "text": "and the iPad knows where you live because of GPS --"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 189260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "which is actually addressed to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 193260.0,
      "text": "The child in me is really excited"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 193260.0,
      "end_time": 195260.0,
      "text": "by these kinds of possibilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 195260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "Now I&#39;ve been talking a lot about magic."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "And I don&#39;t mean wizards and dragons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "I mean the kind of childhood magic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 206260.0,
      "text": "those ideas that we all harbored as children."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 206260.0,
      "end_time": 208260.0,
      "text": "This idea of fireflies in a jar, for some reason,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 208260.0,
      "end_time": 210260.0,
      "text": "was always really exciting to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 210260.0,
      "end_time": 213260.0,
      "text": "And so over here you need to tilt your iPad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 213260.0,
      "end_time": 215260.0,
      "text": "take the fireflies out."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 215260.0,
      "end_time": 218260.0,
      "text": "And they actually illuminate your way through the rest of the book."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "Another idea that really fascinated me as a child"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 226260.0,
      "text": "was that an entire galaxy could be contained"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 226260.0,
      "end_time": 228260.0,
      "text": "within a single marble."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 228260.0,
      "end_time": 230260.0,
      "text": "And so over here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 230260.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "each book and each world"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 232260.0,
      "end_time": 234260.0,
      "text": "becomes a little marble"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 234260.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "that I drag in"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "to this magical device within the device."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "And it opens up a map."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "All along, all fantasy books have always had maps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "but these maps have been static."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "This is a map that grows and glows"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "and becomes your navigation for the rest of the book."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "It reveals itself to you at certain points in the book as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 259260.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m just going to enter in."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 261260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "Another thing that&#39;s actually really important to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "is creating content that is Indian"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 267260.0,
      "end_time": 269260.0,
      "text": "and yet very contemporary."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 271260.0,
      "text": "Over here, these are the Apsaras."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 271260.0,
      "end_time": 274260.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve all heard about fairies and we&#39;ve all heard about nymphs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 274260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "but how many people outside of India"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 280260.0,
      "text": "know about their Indian counterparts, the Apsaras?"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 280260.0,
      "end_time": 284260.0,
      "text": "These poor Apsaras have been trapped inside Indra&#39;s chambers for thousands of years"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 284260.0,
      "end_time": 286260.0,
      "text": "in an old and musty book."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 288260.0,
      "text": "And so we&#39;re bringing them back"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 288260.0,
      "end_time": 291260.0,
      "text": "in a contemporary story for children."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 302260.0,
      "text": "And a story that actually deals with new issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 302260.0,
      "end_time": 304260.0,
      "text": "like the environmental crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 304260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 325260.0,
      "end_time": 329260.0,
      "text": "Speaking of the environmental crisis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 329260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "I think a big problem has been in the last 10 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 332260.0,
      "end_time": 334260.0,
      "text": "is that children have been locked inside their rooms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 334260.0,
      "end_time": 336260.0,
      "text": "glued to their PCs, they haven&#39;t been able to get out."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 336260.0,
      "end_time": 338260.0,
      "text": "But now with mobile technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 338260.0,
      "end_time": 341260.0,
      "text": "we can actually take our children outside into the natural world"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 341260.0,
      "end_time": 343260.0,
      "text": "with their technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 343260.0,
      "end_time": 345260.0,
      "text": "One of the interactions in the book"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 345260.0,
      "end_time": 347260.0,
      "text": "is that you&#39;re sent off on this quest"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 347260.0,
      "end_time": 349260.0,
      "text": "where you need to go outside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 349260.0,
      "end_time": 351260.0,
      "text": "take out your camera on the iPad"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 351260.0,
      "end_time": 353260.0,
      "text": "and collect pictures of different natural objects."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 353260.0,
      "end_time": 355260.0,
      "text": "When I was a child, I had multiple collections"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 355260.0,
      "end_time": 358260.0,
      "text": "of sticks and stones and pebbles and shells."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 358260.0,
      "end_time": 360260.0,
      "text": "And somehow kids don&#39;t do that anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 360260.0,
      "end_time": 362260.0,
      "text": "So in bringing back this childhood ritual,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 362260.0,
      "end_time": 364260.0,
      "text": "you need to go out"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 364260.0,
      "end_time": 366260.0,
      "text": "and, in one chapter, take a picture of a flower"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 368260.0,
      "text": "and then tag it."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 368260.0,
      "end_time": 370260.0,
      "text": "In another chapter, you need to take a picture of a piece of bark"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 370260.0,
      "end_time": 372260.0,
      "text": "and then tag that."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 372260.0,
      "end_time": 374260.0,
      "text": "And what happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 374260.0,
      "end_time": 376260.0,
      "text": "is that you actually create a digital collection of photographs"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 376260.0,
      "end_time": 378260.0,
      "text": "that you can then put up online."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 378260.0,
      "end_time": 380260.0,
      "text": "A child in London puts up a picture of a fox"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 380260.0,
      "end_time": 382260.0,
      "text": "and says, \"Oh, I saw a fox today.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 382260.0,
      "end_time": 384260.0,
      "text": "A child in India says, \"I saw a monkey today.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 384260.0,
      "end_time": 386260.0,
      "text": "And it creates this kind of social network"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 386260.0,
      "end_time": 388260.0,
      "text": "around a collection of digital photographs"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 388260.0,
      "end_time": 390260.0,
      "text": "that you&#39;ve actually taken."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 390260.0,
      "end_time": 393260.0,
      "text": "In the possibilities of linking together"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 393260.0,
      "end_time": 396260.0,
      "text": "magic, the earth and technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 396260.0,
      "end_time": 398260.0,
      "text": "there are multiple possibilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 398260.0,
      "end_time": 400260.0,
      "text": "In the next book, we plan on having an interaction"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 400260.0,
      "end_time": 402260.0,
      "text": "where you take your iPad out with the video on"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 402260.0,
      "end_time": 404260.0,
      "text": "and through augmented reality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 404260.0,
      "end_time": 406260.0,
      "text": "you see this layer of animated pixies"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 406260.0,
      "end_time": 410260.0,
      "text": "appear on a houseplant that&#39;s outside your house."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 410260.0,
      "end_time": 413260.0,
      "text": "At one point, your screen is filled up with leaves."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 413260.0,
      "end_time": 416260.0,
      "text": "And so you need to make the sound of wind and blow them away"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 416260.0,
      "end_time": 418260.0,
      "text": "and read the rest of the book."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 418260.0,
      "end_time": 421260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re moving, we&#39;re all moving here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 421260.0,
      "end_time": 423260.0,
      "text": "to a world where the forces of nature"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 423260.0,
      "end_time": 425260.0,
      "text": "come closer together to technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 425260.0,
      "end_time": 428260.0,
      "text": "and magic and technology can come closer together."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 428260.0,
      "end_time": 431260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re harnessing energy from the sun."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 431260.0,
      "end_time": 434260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re bringing our children and ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 434260.0,
      "end_time": 436260.0,
      "text": "closer to the natural world"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 436260.0,
      "end_time": 438260.0,
      "text": "and that magic and joy"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 438260.0,
      "end_time": 440260.0,
      "text": "and childhood love that we had"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 440260.0,
      "end_time": 442260.0,
      "text": "through the simple medium of a story."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 442260.0,
      "end_time": 444260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 444260.0,
      "end_time": 450260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}